NAME
sws_srv_block - Block the server.
SYNOPSIS
#include <libswocserver.h>

int sws_srv_block();
DESCRIPTION
The sws_srv_block function reads the swoc.conf configuration file and requests
the server to be blocked.
RETURN VALUE
0 on success.
.br
-mge_errno on failure.
ERRORS
On failure mge_errno will be set as required.
